title: Osho_I am that (7 video files)
description:
7 video files , not all from series of talks "I Am That" 1980,
in Buddha hall, Puna, India
talks nr 04, 04, 06, 08, 12, 14, 16
quality of videos are enough good to watch it. 
some questions:

HOW ABOUT TELLING US A LITTLE ESOTERIC BULLSHIT?

... CAN YOU SAY SOMETHING MORE ABOUT THIS DIFFERENCE BETWEEN MAN AND WOMAN AND HOW YOU WORK WITH US IN DIFFERENT WAYS?

HOW DO YOU ALWAYS FIND NEW NAMES TO GIVE TO YOUR SANNYASINS?

FOR DAYS NOW I HAVE BEEN ON FIRE INSIDE. I FEEL THE UNKNOWN IN PART OF ME, AND I AM AFRAID TO JUMP. EVERYTHING IS CUCKOO, AND IT'S BEAUTIFUL AND SCARY AT THE SAME TIME.
PUSH ME, OSHO!ON FIRE,

I WOULD LIKE TO FALL IN LOVE, BUT I AM AFRAID OF BEAUTIFUL WOMEN, AND SO AFRAID OF LOVE, AND I DON'T KNOW WHY.
WHY IS IT SO HARD FOR ME TO FALL IN LOVE?
all audios is possible to download free from oshoworld(dot)com
